        public HintTest.AppliedFix assertOutput(String code)
                                 throws Exception
        Verify the content of the resulting file. Equivalent to assertOutput("test/Test.java"). This method will "normalize" whitespaces in the file: generally, all whitespaces are reduced to a single space both in the given code and the code read from the file, before the comparison.
        Parameters:
        code - expected content of the resulting file.
        Returns:
        the wrapper itself
        Throws:
        AssertionError - if the file does not have the correct content
